Tutorial on adding lock screen widgets:
1.Select and add your favorite widgets
2.In lock screen mode, long press the phone screen to enter the editing mode -> click the Customize button
-> select Lock Screen -> click ADD WIDGETS -> slide to select the LockCanvas application -> select the saved widget

Tutorial on adding dynamic wallpaper:
1.Select your favorite dynamic wallpaper and save it to the album
2.Open the mobile phone album and find the live photo you just saved -> click the share button -> select User as Wallpaper -> click Add




